{"_path":"/latex/lessons/premiere/fonction-exponentielle","_dir":"premiere","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","_id":"content:latex:lessons:premiere:fonction-exponentielle.tex","summary":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"le-nombre-e\">Le nombre <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span></span></span></span></span></h2>\n<p>Le <strong>nombre d’Euler</strong> <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span></span></span></span></span> (également\nappelé constante de Neper) est une constante mathématique irrationnelle\nqui possède de nombreuses propriétés.</p>\n<div id=\"formula-1\" class=\"bubble\" data-variant=\"formula\">\n<h4>Valeur approchée</h4>\n<p>Une valeur approchée de <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span></span></span></span></span> est <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"\\approx 2,71828\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4831em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">≈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">71828</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"la-fonction-exponentielle\">La fonction exponentielle</h2>\n<h3 id=\"definition\">Définition</h3>\n<div id=\"formula-3\" class=\"bubble\" data-variant=\"formula\">\n<h4>Définition</h4>\n<p>La fonction exponentielle notée pour tout <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"x \\in \\mathbb{R}\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6889em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbb\">R</span></span></span></span></span> par <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e^x\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> (ou parfois <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"\\exp(x)\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">exp</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span>) est l’unique fonction <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"f\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span></span>\ndéfinie sur <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"\\mathbb{R}\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6889em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbb\">R</span></span></span></span></span> remplissant les critères\nsuivants :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"f\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span></span> est dérivable sur <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"\\mathbb{R}\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6889em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbb\">R</span></span></span></span></span> et <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"f'\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9463em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7519em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">′</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> = <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"f\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n<li><p><span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"f > 0\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> sur <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"\\mathbb{R}\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6889em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbb\">R</span></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n<li><p><span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"f(0) = 1\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"relations-algebriques\">Relations algébriques</h3>\n<div id=\"formula-4\" class=\"bubble\" data-variant=\"formula\">\n<h4>Relations algébriques</h4>\n<p>La fonction exponentielle a plusieurs propriétés algébriques qu’il\nfaut connaître. Ainsi, pour tous réels <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"x\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span> et <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"y\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></span> :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e^x = e^y \\iff x = y\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6884em;vertical-align:-0.024em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">⟺</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n<li><p><span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e^x < e^y \\iff x < y\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7035em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6884em;vertical-align:-0.024em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">⟺</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"representation-graphique\">Représentation graphique</h3>\n<p>Voici une représentation graphique de la fonction exponentielle\n(courbe bleue) et de sa tangente au point d’abscisse <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"0\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> :</p>\n<div class=\"representation\" data-geogebra-id=\"d62ctre4\"></div>\n<p>On voit plusieurs propriétés données précédemment : <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e^0 = 1\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span>, <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e \\approx 2,718\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4831em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">≈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">718</span></span></span></span></span>, etc. Mais\négalement d’autres propriétés que nous verrons par la suite comme le\nfait que la fonction soit <strong>strictement positive</strong> sur <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"\\mathbb{R}\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6889em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbb\">R</span></span></span></span></span>. À noter que la <strong>tangente</strong> à\nsa courbe représentative en <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"x = 0\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> est <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"y = x + 1\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"etude-de-la-fonction\">Étude de la fonction</h2>\n<h3 id=\"derivee\">Dérivée</h3>\n<div id=\"formula-5\" class=\"bubble\" data-variant=\"formula\">\n<h4>Dérivée d’une composée</h4>\n<p>Soit une fonction <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"u\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">u</span></span></span></span></span> dérivable sur un intervalle\n<span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"I\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">I</span></span></span></span></span>, on a pour tout <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"x\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span> appartenant\nà cet intervalle : <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"(e^{u(x)})' = u'(x)e^{u(x)}\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.138em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.888em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">u</span><span class=\"mopen mtight\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">x</span><span class=\"mclose mtight\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\"><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7519em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">′</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.138em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">u</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7519em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">′</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.888em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">u</span><span class=\"mopen mtight\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">x</span><span class=\"mclose mtight\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"formula-6\" class=\"bubble\" data-variant=\"formula\">\n<h4>Dérivée</h4>\n<p>Ainsi, si pour tout <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"x \\in I\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">I</span></span></span></span></span> on a <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"u(x) = x\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">u</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span>, on retrouve : <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"({e^x})' = e^x\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.0019em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\"><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7519em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">′</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n</div>\n<p>Cette propriété a été donnée dans la section <a href=\"#definition\"><q>Définition</q></a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"variations\">Variations</h3>\n<p>Avec la dérivée donnée précédemment, il est désormais possible\nd’obtenir les variations de la fonction exponentielle.</p>\n<div id=\"formula-7\" class=\"bubble\" data-variant=\"formula\">\n<h4>Variations</h4>\n<div class=\"center\">\n<p><img src=\"/img/lessons/premiere/fonction-exponentielle/variations.svg\" alt=\"variations\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>On remarque sur le tableau de variation que la fonction exponentielle\nest strictement positive et croissante sur <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"\\mathbb{R}\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6889em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbb\">R</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"la-suite-ena\">La suite <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"(e^{na})\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">na</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></h3>\n<div id=\"formula-8\" class=\"bubble\" data-variant=\"formula\">\n\n<p>Soit <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"a \\in \\mathbb{R}\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6889em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbb\">R</span></span></span></span></span>. La suite <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"(e^{na})\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">na</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span> est une suite géométrique de raison <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"e^a\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">a</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> et de premier terme <span class=\"math-rendered\" data-latex=\"1\" data-latex-display=\"false\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n</div>\n\n","level":"premiere","id":"fonction-exponentielle","title":"La fonction exponentielle","chapter":4,"caption":"Les exponentielles sont notamment utilisées dans l’étude des croissances.","description":"La fonction exponentielle est la fonction qui est sa propre dérivée et qui prend la valeur 1 en 0. Elle est utilisée pour modéliser des phénomènes dans lesquels une différence constante sur la variable conduit à un rapport constant sur les images. Dans ce chapitre, on va étudier les propriétés de cette fonction (relations algébriques, dérivées, variations, signe, ...).","difficulty":3,"title-search":"la fonction exponentielle (premiere)","pdf":"/pdf/premiere/fonction-exponentielle.pdf","preview":"/img/lessons/premiere/fonction-exponentielle/preview.jpg","toc":[{"id":"le-nombre-e","text":"Le nombre e","depth":2,"children":[]},{"id":"etude-de-la-fonction","text":"Étude de la fonction","depth":2,"children":[{"id":"derivee","text":"Dérivée","depth":3,"children":[]},{"id":"variations","text":"Variations","depth":3,"children":[]},{"id":"la-suite-ena","text":"La suite (ena)","depth":3,"children":[]}]}],"_source":"content","_file":"latex/lessons/premiere/fonction-exponentielle.tex","_stem":"latex/lessons/premiere/fonction-exponentielle","_extension":"tex"}